arra]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Carmen Garcia Rosado 001.jpg|Private First Class [[Carmen Garc\u00eda Rosado]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Cesar Luis Gonzalez.jpg|First Lieutenant [[C\u00e9sar Luis Gonz\u00e1lez]], U.S. Air Force.\n|File:Denton.jpg|Lieutenant Junior Grade [[Puerto Rican women in the military|Maria Rodriguez Denton]], U.S. Navy. \n|File:Rear Admiral R.C. Benitez.jpg|Rear Admiral [[Rafael Celestino Ben\u00edtez]], U.S. Navy.\n|File:GilbertoMarxuach.JPG|Colonel [[Gilberto Jos\u00e9 Marxuach]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Jose A. Muniz.jpg|Lieutenant Colonel [[Jos\u00e9 Antonio Mu\u00f1iz]], U.S. Air Force. \n|File:Alberto A. Nido jpg..jpg|Brigadier General [[Alberto A. Nido]], U.S. Air Force.\n|File:Antonio Maldonado.jpg|Brigadier General [[Antonio Maldonado]], U.S. Air Force. \n|File:RoseFranco.jpg|Chief Warrant Officer [[Rose Franco]], U.S. Marine Corps.\n|File:Carlos Betances.JPG|Colonel [[Carlos Betances Ram\u00edrez]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Antonio Rodriguez Balinas.jpg|Brigadier General [[Antonio Rodr\u00edguez Balinas]], U.S. Army.\n|File:ModestoCartagena3.jpg|Sergeant First Class [[Modesto Cartagena]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Demensio Rivera.jpg|Private [[Demensio Rivera]], U.S. Army. \n|File:Juan-negron-united-states-army-medal-of-honor.jpg|Master Sergeant [[Juan E. Negr\u00f3n]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Miguel-vera-united-states-army-medal-of-honor.jpg|Private Miguel Vera, U.S. Army.\n|File:Fernando Luis Garcia.JPG|Private First Class [[Fernando Luis Garc\u00eda]], U.S. Marine Corps.\n|File:Horacio Rivero Jr.jpg|Admiral [[Horacio Rivero, Jr.]], U.S. Navy.\n|File:AcostaRosario.jpg|Private First Class [[Humberto Acosta-Rosario]], U.S. Army.\n|File:Diego E. Hernandez.jpeg|Vice Admiral [[Diego E. Hern\u00e1ndez]], U.S. Navy.\n|File:Felices se.jpg|Major General [[Salvador Felices]], U.S. Air Force.\n|File:Carlos Lozada.JPG|Private First Class [[Carlos Lozada]], U.S. Army.\n|File:AngelMendez2.jpg|Sergeant [[Angel Mendez]], U.S. Marine Corps.\n|File: Ram\u00f3n N\u00fa\u00f1ez-Ju\u00e1rez.